  "intent": "Execute library index PCR for Zymo-Seq RiboFree Total RNA library preparation: Transfer 5\u00b5L UDI primers from index plate to thermocycler samples using multichannel pipette with 3x 15\u00b5L mixing. Add 15\u00b5L then 10\u00b5L Taq premix to each sample with 3x 15\u00b5L final mixing. Run thermocycler protocol with initial 95\u00b0C/10min denaturation, followed by 10-13 cycles (based on RNA input amount) of 95\u00b0C/30sec, 60\u00b0C/30sec, 72\u00b0C/1min, then final extension 72\u00b0C/7min. Post-PCR, add 50\u00b5L elution buffer with 5x 15\u00b5L mixing.",
